  "description": "A truly large and roomy premium-class two-chamber refrigerator, presented on the market by the popular Bosch brand in 2023 and positioned by the manufacturer in the upper price segment. The stainless steel body has a matte coating with AntiFinger protection against rapid contamination. The capacity of the device is 631 liters. The refrigeration chamber holds 479 liters, and the freezer located below holds 152 liters. The refrigeration compartment has a combined drawer with a freshness zone. Additionally, the Bosch KGN86AIDR refrigerator is equipped with a double VitaFresh plus container, designed for loading fruits with vegetables and herbs. This model has an inverter with an intelligent power control system for the device. For added convenience, you can set the freezing and cooling modes remotely. Each of the working chambers has a separate circulation circuit. It is also worth paying attention to the fact that this device can be placed close to walls and furniture. Light and sound alarms for open doors and incorrect operation of the cooling system are available. The control panel touch block is located on the upper door. And with all this, the refrigerator has a fairly optimized power supply - electricity consumption is only 246 kWh per year.",
